data.description: This Mountain’s Edge home is within close proximity to restaurants and shopping. This home has been recently upgraded, a must-see. Located on a cul-de-sac and corner lot, this move-in ready home features 4 beds, 2  1/2 baths, a master suite w/ dual sinks, a walk-in closet, a spacious formal living/dining room, & a welcoming Great room with new Vinal plank flooring downstairs and new Engineered hardwood on the second floor. This home also has Plantation shutters on all windows. and on the slider. An Open kitchen with stainless steel appliances upgraded double-stacked cabinets & island. This home also has a large Koi pond in the backyard.
